v2.3.2 [20 Mar 2018]
- Added getitem, setItem, replace
- Updated "validFields" so that if query parameter in not a valid field for table, an error will be thrown instead of ignoring field for update/delete query

v2.3.1 [22 Mar 2015]
- Added support for 'distinct' queries

v2.3 [13 Mar 2014]
- Added multi-field sorting capabilities to query()
- Added queryAll(), an alias to query() that takes a dict of params instead of positional arguments
- Made localStorageDB AMD compatible
- Fixed null value update bug

v2.2 [27 Jan 2014]
- Added tableFields()
- query() now supports a start parameter for offsetting
- Changed validateName() to accept integer types as field, table, db names

v2.1 [19 Nov 2013]
- Added alterTable()

v2.0 [12 Jun 2013]
- Minor bug fixes including better IE8 compatibility